    <briefdescription>
<para>Generates delegates according to the specified signature on runtime. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>There are limitations of this generator:<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>It can only hook to Events that have a Delegate of type void (for example EventHandler)</para></listitem><listitem><para>It uses <ref refid="namespace_system_1_1_reflection" kindref="compound">Reflection</ref> so it cannot be used in XBAPs because of the security restrictions there are in XBAPs. </para></listitem></orderedlist>
</para>    </detaileddescription>
